                <p style="color: var(--text-muted); line-height: 1.4;">
                    Click and hold inside a block card to start breaking it. The breaking delta speed calculation responds dynamically to your active tool matching the block's requirements. Unbreakable blocks stay safe.
                </p>
            </div>
        </div>

        <div class="grid-container" id="blocks-grid"></div>
    </div>

